{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AgsHxD6mRfGf9qPPDoX9cF","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here is a summary of what was done and what was found.\n\n---\n\n## QA Eval — F5 Sprint 1\n\n### Phase A results (all pass)\n\n| Check | Result |\n|-------|--------|\n| `src/app/api/events/route.ts` exports `POST` | PASS — `export async function POST` at line 3 |\n| `pnpm test` | PASS — 45 passed, 16 skipped, 0 failures across 5 test files |\n| `pnpm lint` | PASS — Biome checked 25 files, exit 0 |\n| `pnpm typecheck` | PASS — `tsc --noEmit` clean, exit 0 |\n| `pnpm build` | PASS — Turbopack compiled, `/api/events` appears as a dynamic route |\n\n### Phase B (integration gap)\n\nClickHouse was not running at `localhost:8123` (connection refused). Dev server was also not running. Both are required for integration HTTP tests. These criteria are marked infrastructure-blocked, not code failures.\n\n### Files written\n\n- `/Users/riccardocaranfil/bitrefill/minipanel-blank-night-2/src/app/api/events/__tests__/route.integration.test.ts` — 3 integration tests using `fetch()` against `http://localhost:3000/api/events`, with a `beforeAll` server-availability check that logs a warning and returns early (does not hard-fail) when the dev server is unreachable. Passes `pnpm test` and `pnpm lint` cleanly.\n- `/Users/riccardocaranfil/bitrefill/minipanel-blank-night-2/features/F5-eval-1.md` — eval file\n\n### Verdict: APPROVED — Score 9/10\n\nAll Phase A criteria pass. One point withheld because integration HTTP scenarios could not be verified due to ClickHouse not running. The integration tests are in place and will execute automatically once `pnpm dev` brings up the full stack."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: aa7eaebac75085b03 (use SendMessage with to: 'aa7eaebac75085b03' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 30378\ntool_uses: 24\nduration_ms: 100193</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6abd9b3b-4269-43d